Changelog SWISS

1.0.0
Added link to changelog for auto updating
Added Curseforge and Modrinth auto updating (created modrinth project)
Added recipes for the interfaces
Improved the join network screen (inside panel, this should probably replace the other screen in all other blocks)

0.3.0
Added changelog file
Changed import and export texture screen (removed the scroll bar)
Added MousePositionManagerUtil allows to restore the mouse position after a screen change
Mouse positions no longer reset when changing screen inside a screen
Added mod_description and mod_authors to properties file
